@c         [x, -3, 3], [y, -2, 2]])$
@c ===end===
@example
(%i1) plot3d ([2^(-x^2 + y^2), 4*sin(3*(x^2+y^2))/(x^2+y^2),
              [x, -3, 3], [y, -2, 2]])$
@end example

@ifnotinfo
@image{../figures/plotting16,8cm}
@end ifnotinfo

