@c plot3d ([[2^(-x^2 + y^2),[x,-2,2],[y,-2,2]],
@c    4*sin(3*(x^2+y^2))/(x^2+y^2),
@c    [x, -3, 3], [y, -2, 2]], [plot_format,xmaxima])$
@c ===end===
@example
@group
